Class TransformCompareWithTransformResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.kb.xml.transformassert.TransformCompareWithTransformResults
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransformResults

    public class TransformCompareWithTransformResults
extends Object
implements TransformResults
    An instance of this class is returned by TransformCompareWithTransformers.whenTransforming(File, String...)

    It exposes assertion methods to do comparisons between the XML outputted by both stylesheets
